Fix Makefile.micro for proper microperl 5.38 build

The original Makefile.micro has several issues:
1. Compiles regcomp.c multiple times creating duplicate symbols
2. Missing new source files required by Perl 5.38 (class.c, builtin.c)
3. Missing stub implementations for unsupported features in PERL_MICRO

This patch removes the duplicate regcomp compilation units and adds
the necessary source files with proper compilation.

